author: Andrea Park CBS News
title: Whitney Port shares wedding picture
text:
Whitney Port is now Mrs. Rosenman.
32 Photos Knots See which stars have popped the question and said "I do"
The former reality star of "The Hills" and "The City" tied the knot to producer Tim Rosenman , who she met when she was filming "The City." The two started dating in 2012 and got engaged in 2013.
Port was spare on details, simply posting a photo of herself with the caption "Mrs. Rosenman" on Instagram.
The photo is shot only from the chest up, but you can see that the fashion designer is wearing a strapless white gown and a delicate gold necklace. Port also had her hair in a loosely braided updo.
